    Golden pools~

    Burr comb is common. Bees like to fill the gaps between boxes and frames as they deem fit. Theyll fill these cells with drone comb and resources.

    When we go to do an inspection these combs tear open and the bees promptly begin feasting, nothing goes to waste.
